com.yandex.money.api.time

Class DateTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yandex.money.api.time.DateTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<DateTime>

    public final class DateTime
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<DateTime>
    Represents a date-time value that is backed up by a Calendar instance. The implementation of this class is immutable.
    See Also:
    Calendar
